%% Data Science Pipelines - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant UI as ds-pipeline-ui<br/>React Frontend
    participant API as ds-pipeline<br/>API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant S3 as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/TCP
    participant Tekton as Tekton API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant MW as metadata-writer
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>Route: HTTPS/443 (TLS Reencrypt)
    Route->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>OpenShift OAuth
    OAuthProxy->>UI: Authenticated request
    UI->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines/upload<br/>HTTP/8888 (plaintext)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306 (Username/Password)
    API->>S3: Store pipeline package<br/>HTTP/9000 (AccessKey/SecretKey)
    API-->>UI: Pipeline created

    User->>Route: Create Run
    Route->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS/8443
    OAuthProxy->>UI: Authenticated
    UI->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>HTTP/8888
    API->>DB: Store run metadata
    API->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)
    Tekton-->>API: PipelineRun created
    API-->>UI: Run started

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Run Status Persistence

    PA->>Tekton: Watch PipelineRuns<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)
    Tekton-->>PA: PipelineRun status update
    PA->>API: Report status<br/>HTTP/8888

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Execution

    SWC->>Tekton: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)
    SWC->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun on schedule<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA token)

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 4: ML Metadata Tracking

    MW->>MLMD: Write execution metadata<br/>gRPC/8080 (plaintext)
    MLMD->>DB: Store metadata<br/>MySQL/3306 (Username/Password)
